    <text>
        <front>
            <div type="summary">
                <p>
                   This letter sent by Hogarth Press is an answer for Editorial Montanesa about the Spanish rights of Mr Kitchin's books
                </p>
            </div>
        </front>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <placeName>
                            Madrid, Spain
                        </placeName>
                        <date when="1947-12-02">
                            02 December 1947
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>
                            <orgName>Editorial Montanesa</orgName>
                        </addrLine>
                        <addrLine>
                            Fernandes de la Rios 4,
                        </addrLine>
                        <addrLine>
                            Madrid, Spain.
                        </addrLine>
                    </address>
                    <salute>
                        Dear Sirs,
                    </salute>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    Thank you for your letter<lb/>
                    24 November enquiring for the Spanish rights in Mr Kitchin's<lb/>
                    books. We only hold the rights<lb/>
                    in one of these &apos;Death of My Aunt&apos;<lb/>
                    and the Spanish rights in this title<lb/>
                    are already sold. For the rights<lb/>
                    in his other books, you should apply<lb/>
                    to Mr. Kitchin's agents, <unclear>Messrs</unclear>. Pearn<lb/>
                    Pellinger &amp; Higham, Ltd., 39/40<lb/>
                    Bedford Street, Strand, London, W.C.2.<lb/>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>
                        Yours faithfully,</lb>
                    </salute>
                    <seg>
                        For the Hogarth Press Ltd.
                    </seg>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
